    "Id": "chassisdef_coriolis_CRLS-586",
    "Name": "Coriolis",
    "Details": "The CRLS-586 replaces the heavy autocannons of earlier variants with twin Rotary AC/5s, shifting the Coriolis away from single devastating strikes toward sustained high-volume fire. A Targeting Computer sharpens everything on the frame while an ER Large Laser and ER Medium Laser cover range brackets the autocannons cannot reach. CASE protects both ammunition bays and an Anti-Missile System adds defensive depth. Three jump jets keep the chassis signature ambush potential fully intact.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Accurate Weapon - AC</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.16</color></b>\n\n<color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limit: Right Lower</color>",
