  "StockRole": "Close Assault",
  "YangsThoughts": "This thing dates back to 2501, which means it was already ancient when the Star League collapsed. New Earth Trading Company built it, Earthwerks kept producing it, and somehow examples survived all the way to now. The jump jets on an assault mech that size were a big deal when it was new and honestly they still are. Getting one of these out of salvage is finding a piece of history that can still punch a hole through most of what it faces.",
